'''Amer Rasem Adel Jamous''' ({{langx|ar|عَامِر رَاسِم عَادِل جَامُوس}}; born 3 July 2002) is a [[Jordan]]ian professional [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder (association football)|midfielder]] for  [[Iraq Stars League]] club [[Al-Zawraa SC|Al-Zawraa]], on loan from [[Al-Wehdat SC|Al-Wehdat]], as well as the [[Jordan national football team|Jordan national team]].

==Club career==
===Al-Jazeera===
Amer Jamous began his career at [[Al-Jazeera SC (Amman)|Al-Jazeera]], and was noted to have been a consistent starter for the club.<ref>{{cite web |title=صدارة مهددة للحسين .. الوحدات والفيصلي بدون عنوان .. والعقبة بفوز مثير |url=https://www.rumonline.net/print.php?id=610961 |website=rumonline.net |publisher=Rum Online |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=22 May 2022}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=الوحدات يحتفظ بالصدارة بفوز صعب على الجزيرة |url=https://palsport.com/article/48396 |website=palsport.com |publisher=Pal Sport |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=30 July 2022}}</ref>

====Al-Wehdat (loan)====
[[Al-Wehdat SC|Al-Wehdat]] began to show interest in Jamous since 11 December 2022,<ref>{{cite web |title=مجالس رياضية أردنية.. أنس يلوح بتقديم شكوى.. الوحدات يرغب بضم جاموس.. الحاج يعود إلى عمان وعرض مصري لخالد صياحين |url=https://alsaa.net/article/225083/%D9%85%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3-%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D9%86%D8%B3 |website=alsaa.net |publisher=Al-Sa'aa |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=11 December 2022}}</ref> with [[Al-Hussein SC (Irbid)|Al-Hussein]] and [[Al-Faisaly SC (Amman)|Al-Faisaly]] joining the race as well in the following month.<ref>{{cite web |title=العجالين يقترب من الأولى السعودي..عرض جزائري وسعودي للعوضات و حلفان مجلس إدارة نادي بعدم كشف التعاقدات مجالس رياضية |url=https://alsaa.net/article/227263/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%8A%D9%82%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84%D9%89 |website=alsaa.net |publisher=Al-Sa'aa |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=1 January 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=جاموس يقترب من الفيصلي |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1205620 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=15 January 2023}}</ref> Jamous eventually agreed to move to Al-Wehdat on a season-long loan deal from Al-Jazeera on 25 January 2023, to which he was moved due to financial constraints on Al-Jazeera's end after getting relegated to the [[2023 Jordan League Division 1|Jordanian First Division League]].<ref>{{cite web |title=الجزيرة يعير جاموس للوحدات |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1208599 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=25 January 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=الجزيرة يوافق على إعارة لاعبه جاموس إلى الوحدات |url=https://royanews.tv/news/334724 |website=royanews.tv |publisher=Ro'ya News |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=25 January 2023}}</ref> In an interview, Jamous stated that Al-Wehdat had shown a greater interest towards him, as opposed to Al-Hussein or Al-Faisaly.<ref>{{cite web |title=جاموس لـ 'مدار الساعة': حظيت باهتمام كبير من الوحدات ومتعطش للالقاب واسعاد الجماهير وهذه رسالتي للجزيرة |url=https://c/article/230162/%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3-%D9%84%D9%80-%D9%85%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A9 |website=جاموس لـ 'مدار الساعة': حظيت باهتمام كبير من الوحدات ومتعطش للالقاب واسعاد الجماهير وهذه رسالتي للجزيرة |publisher=Al-Sa'aa |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=28 January 2023}}</ref> The loan deal was valued at approximately 50 thousand [[Jordanian dinar|dinars]].<ref>{{cite web |title=مجالس رياضية اردنية.. الرازم يغادر الأردن.. الزلزال يهدد احتراف لاعبين أردنيين.. وتعثر انتقال ابو شعيرة للدوري العراقي والوحدات في مقر نادي الجزيرة.. الخميس |url=https://alsaa.net/article/231256/%D9%85%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3-%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B2%D9%85 |website=alsaa.net |publisher=Al-Sa'aa |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=8 February 2023}}</ref> The deal was finalized on 10 February 2023.<ref>{{cite web |title=الوحدات ينجز صفقة جاموس.. غدا |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1213316 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=9 February 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=بهاء فيصل يعود إلى عمان .. والوحدات ينجز صفقة جاموس |url=https://www.addustour.com/articles/1329973-%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%81%D9%8A%D8%B5%D9%84-%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%B9%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%8A%D9%86%D8%AC%D8%B2-%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%82%D8%A9-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3 |website=addustour.com |publisher=Ad-Dustor |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=11 February 2023}}</ref>

On 18 May 2023, Jamous was at the center of a heated exchange, when [[Al-Hussein SC (Irbid)|Al-Hussein]] goalkeeper [[Abdullah Al-Zubi]] confronted the player, after Jamous had stopped an Al-Hussein counterattack.<ref>{{cite web |title=تدافع بين لاعبي الوحدات والحسين إربد (فيديو) |url=https://www.ammonnews.net/article/766541 |website=ammonnews.net |publisher=Ammon News |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=18 May 2023}}</ref>

Jamous was a contributor to Al-Wehdat's winning [[2023–24 Jordan FA Cup]] run, after defeating [[Al-Hussein SC (Irbid)|Al-Hussein]].<ref>{{cite web |last1=Abu Ahmed |first1=Youssef |title=الوحدات يحتفظ باللقب على حساب الحسين إربد |url=https://www.addustour.com/articles/1426941-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%AA%D9%81%D8%B8-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%84%D9%82%D8%A8-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%A5%D8%B1%D8%A8%D8%AF |website=addustour.com |publisher=Ad-Dustor |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=30 June 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Al-Shaibani|first1=Tha'er|title=عامر جاموس لكووورة: الوحدات كان بأمس الحاجة إلى هذا اللقب |url=https://m.kooora.com/?n=1338195 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=1 July 2024}}</ref>

====Brief return to Al-Jazeera====
After completing his season-long move, Jamous returned to Al-Jazeera, who have since regained promotion to the [[2024–25 Jordanian Pro League|Jordanian Pro League]]. His return was short-lived, as Al-Jazeera continued to suffer from financial strains, and therefore had to offload players.<ref>{{cite web |title="التمكين المالي" يحرم الجزيرة من 8 لاعبين أمام الحسين إربد |url=https://alghad.com/Section-180/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D9%85%D9%83%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%B1%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%86-8-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%A3%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%A5%D8%B1%D8%A8%D8%AF-1783168 |website=alghad.com |publisher=Al-Ghad |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=10 August 2024}}</ref> Al-Wehdat would then negotiate with Al-Jazeera to retain Jamous, this time on a permanent contract.<ref>{{cite web |title=تفاصيل مفاوضات الوحدات لضم جاموس |url=https://www.khaberni.com/news/%D8%AA%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8A%D9%84-%D9%85%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B6%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%84%D8%B6%D9%85-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3-670422 |website=khaberni.com |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=25 August 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=تفاصيل مفاوضات الوحدات لضم جاموس |url=https://jfranews.com.jo/article/465836 |website=jfranews.com |publisher=Jfra News |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=25 August 2024}}</ref>

===Al-Wehdat===
On 2 September 2024, Jamous returned to [[Al-Wehdat SC|Al-Wehdat]], after Al-Jazeera agreed on a deal ranging between 50 and 65 thousand [[Jordanian dinar|dinars]]. This time, signing on a permanent contract lasting for three seasons.<ref>{{cite web |title=الوحدات يضم عامر جاموس من الجزيرة |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1352295 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=2 September 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Amer Jamous |url=https://alghad.com/Section-143/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9-%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A9/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%8A%D8%B8%D9%81%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%AE%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A9-1802517 |website=alghad.com |publisher=Al-Ghad |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=3 September 2024}}</ref> He stated in an interview that he hopes to win trophies for Al-Wehdat, as well as represent his national team at the World Cup.<ref>{{cite web |title=جاموس يتحدث لـ"الغد" عن طموحاته مع الوحدات وفرص المنتخب الوافرة في بلوغ المونديال |url=https://alghad.com/Section-180/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3-%D9%8A%D8%AA%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%AB-%D9%84%D9%80-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%BA%D8%AF-%D8%B9%D9%86-%D8%B7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%87-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%88%D9%81%D8%B1%D8%B5-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%84%D9%88%D8%BA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%88%D9%86%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%84-1804486 |website=alghad.com |publisher=Al-Ghad |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=5 September 2024}}</ref>

====Al-Zawraa (loan)====
On 23 January 2026, Jamous joined [[Iraq Stars League]] club [[Al-Zawraa SC|Al-Zawraa]] on a short loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=الزوراء يحسم صفقة عامر جاموس بعد ماراثون من المفاوضات |url=https://royanews.tv/news/371760/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B2%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%85-%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%82%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3-%D8%A8%D8%B9%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AB%D9%88%D9%86-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B6%D8%A7%D8%AA |website=royanews.tv |publisher=Roya News |access-date=30 January 2026 |language=Arabic |date=23 January 2026}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Murad |first1=Mohammad |title=عامر جاموس يكشف أسباب الانتقال إلى الزوراء |url=https://www.winwin.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3-%D9%8A%D9%83%D8%B4%D9%81-%D8%A3%D8%B3%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B2%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%A1?amp |website=winwin.com |publisher=WinWin |access-date=30 January 2026 |language=Arabic |date=26 January 2026}}</ref>

==International career==
Jamous was a youth international for Jordan,<ref>{{cite web|title=التعادل 2-2 يحسم مواجهة المنتخب الوطني تحت 23 عاما مع نظيره الفلسطيني|url=https://www.almamlakatv.com/news/108587- |website=almamlakatv.com |publisher=Al-Mamlaka |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=23 December 2022}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=المنتخب الأولمبي يكتفي بالتعادل مع فلسطين وديا |url=https://menafn.com/arabic/1105347810/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%94%D9%88%D9%84%D9%85%D8%A8%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D9%83%D8%AA%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D9%81%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%B7%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A7 |website=menafn.com |publisher=MENA FN |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=23 December 2022}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=إيران تقصي الأردن من بطولة غرب آسيا |url=https://mawazin.net/Details.aspx?jimare=229587 |website=mawazin.net |publisher=Mawazin |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=18 June 2023}}</ref> having represented the Jordanian [[Jordan national under-23 football team|under-23]] team at the [[2024 AFC U-23 Asian Cup]] that took place in Qatar.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.jfa.jo/news.php?id=29736&title=%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%B7%D9%86%D9%8A-%D8%AA23-%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%86-%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%85%D8%AA%D9%87-%D9%84%D8%A8%D8%B7%D9%88%D9%84%D8%A9-%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D8%A2%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%A7-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A9|title=إعلان القائمة الأولية للمنتخب الوطني ت23 لمعسكر قطر والنهائيات الآسيوية|trans-title=Announcing the preliminary list of the U23 national team for the Qatar camp and the Asian Cup finals|publisher=Jordan Football Association|date=6 April 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=التعادل يسيطر على مواجهة الأولمبي مع أستراليا |url=https://assabeel.net/news/2024/4/16/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%84-%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%B7%D8%B1-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%85%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%84%D9%85%D8%A8%D9%8A-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A7 |website=assabeel.net |publisher=As-Sabeel |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=15 April 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title="أولمبي الكرة" يودع كأس آسيا وأبو زمع يؤكد تحمله المسؤولية |url=https://alrai.com/article/10832245/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84%D9%85%D8%A8%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%AF%D8%B9-%D9%83%D8%A3%D8%B3-%D8%A2%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%A7-%D9%88%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B2%D9%85%D8%B9-%D9%8A%D8%A4%D9%83%D8%AF-%D8%AA%D8%AD%D9%85%D9%84%D9%87-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B3%D8%A4%D9%88%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A9 |website=alrai.com |publisher=Al-Rai |access-date=12 October 2024 |language=Arabic |date=22 April 2024}}</ref>

